    "deskripsi_bisnis": "PT. Mandom Indonesia Tbk manufactures and sells cosmetics and other products in Indonesia. It offers hair care, skin care and make-up, body care, and face care products, as well as perfumes, cleansing materials, and plastic containers. The company markets its products under the GATSBY, PIXY, PUCELLE, MIRATONE, LUCIDO-L, MANDOM, Tancho, JOHNNY ANDREAN, SPALDING, GLAZELLE de Pucelle, Color Comm., Fresh n fresh, LOVILLEA, and STYLE UP brands. It sells its products in the United Arab Emirates, Malaysia, Japan, Thailand, the Philippines, Singapore, Korea, Vietnam, Hongkong, India, and Taiwan. The company was formerly known as PT Tancho Indonesia and changed its name to PT. Mandom Indonesia Tbk in 2001. The company was incorporated in 1969 and is headquartered in Jakarta, Indonesia. PT. Mandom Indonesia Tbk operates as a subsidiary of Mandom Corporation.",
